-----Original Message-----
From: Michelle Harper [mailto:earthmagik@...]
Sent: Monday, June 12, 2000 12:06 PM
To: Unschooling-dotcom@egroups.com
Subject: [Unschooling-dotcom] Great replies

Hi All!  Thanks everyone for replying to the Meeting new people post....It was great for me...I had alot of fun reading about others on the list.....it seems we all have alot in common......I am an avid breast feeding supporter, although I am not a part of LLL.......My husband had a friend who was a UU member, and I heard it was  pretty diverse, and positive.. I appreciated being able to look at an official UU site....there's actually a local church in Edmonds, and we're considering giving it a visit...I really liked the part about religtion being within someone, rather than without.......and respecting everyone's right to persue their own spiritual path, no matter what that may be, and their community, and global activism, and participation....Just Great.......Also, there was a member on the list from North , here in Washington, that I wanted to touch base with..I think your name is Tiffany..sounded like we had some common interests, if you'd like to get together sometime.......It was reallly neat seeing where you are all located all around the U.S., and in Portugal, and other spots abroad....it's inspiring to have members from all over the globe.......SO keep it coming...I also found myself nodding my head going"yah, us too, us too!"..Well we've found the magician for our ds's birthday party in July.....he does the doves appearing and all.....sounds like we'll have great fun.......Thanks for all your input!!!!! Many Blessings All!   Michelle
